{"tid":2285901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以色列特工在伊朗擊殺阿蓋達二號人物","createTime":"2020-11-14T13:27:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T13:53:43.000Z","uid":64191,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"65e0582f971c434b28aa63b0498ca45297834931","tid":2285901,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:27:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202011140046.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202011140046.aspx&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=59fc5bb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202011140046.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>（中央社華盛頓13日綜合外電報導）紐約時報（New York Times）報導，以色列特工今年8月7日依美國指示，在伊朗擊斃極端組織蓋達的二把手，此人被控在幕後協助策劃1998年美國駐非洲兩處大使館炸彈攻擊案。<br />\n<br />\n紐時今天引述情報官員的說法報導，3個多月前，兩名騎摩托車的男子在伊朗首都德黑蘭開槍擊斃蓋達組織（Al-Qaeda）的阿布杜拉（Abdullah Ahmed Abdullah），他平常使用的假名是馬士禮（Abu Muhammad al-Masri）。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，出生於埃及的馬士禮被視為蓋達組織現任首腦薩瓦里（Ayman al-Zawahri）可能的繼任者，他身亡的消息隱瞞到今天才為人所知。目前還不清楚美國在這場擊殺案中扮演什麼角色。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMossad又做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34a35a4ab96e7e7f5ba3cc362cd916091cc3533","tid":2285901,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有幾多連登仔戒唔到TVB 譯名「阿你蓋達」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cf6177cc9b93637d57fceaff7c1c96da111015","tid":2285901,"uid":97078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:40:06.000Z","msg":"22年後先殺到...."},{"pid":"2df6bad464ac1d6cd10c6781f1b7baa9837ccb71","tid":2285901,"uid":154486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"21cf6177cc9b9363